Rho (aka ρ)
===========

## Architecture

+-------------------------------------+
|               runtime               |
| +---------+ +---------+ +---------+ |
| | context | | context | | context | |
| | (stack) | | (stack) | | (stack) | |
| +---------+ +---------+ +---------+ |
+-------------------------------------+

## Goals

  * Stack-base bytecode VM
  * Lexical scoping
  * Native concurrency
  * Embeddable in C/C艹.
    Optional GC


